{"tid":1159653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日62名學生妹場邊加油！下體突「發癢」送醫　原因竟是…","createTime":"2019-05-18T00:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T02:25:21.000Z","uid":32511,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"912b7871c33ac6346450634eb29fe3e1e6257fe7","tid":1159653,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T00:43:41.000Z","msg":"日本滋賀縣中學春季綜合體育大會，16日上午10點在大津市皇子山綜合運動公園展開軟網賽事，沒想到，現場有7校中學共計62名到場觀賽的女國中生，加油到一半「下體突然發癢」，甚至大腿及臀部出現紅疹等現象，最後通通被送醫治療。<br />\n <br />\n綜合日媒報導，大津市7所初中16日在大津市皇子山綜合運動公園的網球場進行比賽，不料當日坐在場邊長凳上觀賽加油的62位女學生，下體卻突然發癢，大腿、臀部紛紛出現紅疹，且伴隨著陣陣疼痛感，讓校方趕緊將女學生送往附近醫院救治。<br />\n <br />\n報導指出，該起事件起因，疑似是長凳上的塗裝物質，具有刺激性所導致，幸好62名女學生送醫已無大礙，目前大津市已停用現場的長凳，並全面檢查市內是否還有用同塗料的設施。"},{"pid":"5446fe1d331a6ff061d2a8d2730e60e1dbcf553e","tid":1159653,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T00:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7b7c061bf67c7cb8814652e50ee90c0b703726","tid":1159653,"uid":41846,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T00:47:14.000Z","msg":"又係av好題材<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdf1b45e38d61805e60b444054208b9e2208bea","tid":1159653,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:02:08.000Z","msg":"企劃？"},{"pid":"3e037b9ebfac21d51e4a11b13431d98900822819","tid":1159653,"uid":71913,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:20:23.000Z","msg":"如果係會讓人發情既物料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" cl